{"tid":782413,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"到底西裝褸條線洗唔洗剪？","createTime":"2018-08-16T17:00:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T10:51:56.000Z","uid":61465,"like":1,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"db01807e73442258d8a8bbe3019e74e27b920175","tid":782413,"uid":61465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T17:00:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/17/005709_9af4ecf79685d6417a3a5718680e942a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F17%2F005709_9af4ecf79685d6417a3a5718680e942a.png&h=3d27649c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n白色果條線到底有咩用？<br />\n我見鋪頭啲model 公仔著住無剪，但條線又車得好求其<br />\n大家會唔會剪走佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪有咩時裝文化野我唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n剪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔剪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d58439aabf3bc1043356155c3c3cb51e096720c","tid":782413,"uid":61465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T17:37:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f04982c3fd9a5f34469151eafe5d32add87ee3e7","tid":782413,"uid":199679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T17:45:09.000Z","msg":"試下剪咗佢，睇吓有咩事會發生再同我地講聲<br />\n如果最後奶嘢就再縫返囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3fefa6ae7f9cfd79919f5489f6f6e1db329a948","tid":782413,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T17:49:03.000Z","msg":"唔洗，以前靚野純手工先有條線，不過而家變左裝飾，唔鐘意挑走都無影響"},{"pid":"cc51891c71529fba560af279123d74c1691cc457","tid":782413,"uid":100760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T19:11:36.000Z","msg":"去啲著西裝嘅場合就係靠條線認邊啲真係有錢佬，邊啲係窮撚"},{"pid":"b873e593e2b7c14642e4e8ad1d3f7df33534bf6b","tid":782413,"uid":61465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T01:28:46.000Z","msg":"剪左，點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb8eece7acd3281ea903bdf6a17db8fb238d0f8","tid":782413,"uid":3838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b873e593e2b7c14642e4e8ad1d3f7df33534bf6b","tid":782413,"uid":61465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T01:28:46.000Z","msg":"剪左，點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T01:55:09.000Z","msg":"買過件"},{"pid":"a2e07fbfea9cdac49102ef15066ef0277ea2231e","tid":782413,"uid":61465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e255f4f94182031092b3ce046993d8b8a310ea","tid":782413,"uid":39064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:51:56.000Z","msg":"買帽都唔會搣走個貼紙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}